I figured it was high
time for us to relive

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:23.520
our newlywed days.

00:00:23.610 --> 00:00:25.280
You suck, old man.

00:00:25.360 --> 00:00:28.570
[NARRATOR] Meanwhile, Ami and
Sakaki invited Uzaki

00:00:28.650 --> 00:00:30.360
out for drinks.

00:00:30.450 --> 00:00:32.910
Not to change the subject,
but I've always been curious

00:00:32.990 --> 00:00:34.870
to learn what you were
like back in high school.

00:00:34.950 --> 00:00:36.700
You wanna give us the backstory?

00:00:36.790 --> 00:00:38.040
[UZAKI]
Huh?

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:15.090
[UZAKI]
Another swim lesson, huh?

00:02:15.180 --> 00:02:17.060
How many times has
Sakurai stayed after

00:02:17.140 --> 00:02:20.180
