won't hold it against you.

00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:25.200
[UZAKI]
So, I was wondering.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:27.780
You said you only started
swimming in high school, right?

00:05:27.870 --> 00:05:29.960
Did you play any sports
in middle school?

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:31.880
[SAKURAI] I was on the
baseball team for a while,

00:05:31.960 --> 00:05:33.630
but I quit after a year.

00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:35.550
