clubs after that.

00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:37.050
[UZAKI]
No? Why not?

00:05:37.130 --> 00:05:40.050
[SAKURAI] I dunno. Maybe they
just weren't my thing.

00:05:40.130 --> 00:05:41.510
[UZAKI]
Is that so?

00:05:41.590 --> 00:05:43.380
